reviews.text: Food and price are on the average

Poor service and aweful food! We won't visit it again for sure. I ordered a club sandwich and can't believe it takes over 20 mins for a "warm" sandwich. During the waiting, I tracing with a staff however he insisted the sandwich will take longer time as they need to toast the bread. How come the sandwich is warm but not hot. Worse than a local cafes.
Food is no good, average service.
second try on the iced drip coffee, last time is in shatin, still no good compare to years ago. guess it is tombstoned.
Very Good

reviews.text: 試了下午茶，可以呀！下次試埋佢的扒，再評。
原本對佢都幾有期望，見佢成日有咁多人喺度排隊，但係食落又唔覺得有咩咁特別，而且餐牌款式好少，基本上除咗牛扒都冇乜嘢好食
今天員工心情麻麻！態度勁差。每人$2xx幾食午餐都唔算係平！
只有牛扒，拉麵……選擇太少！食物味道吾得！失望！
連鎖店式cafe ㄧ貫水準還可以
